statement.p:
Find a basis for the subspace of M_{2,2} W=\mathrm{span}\ \left\{\left[\begin{array}{cc}
-2 & -3 \\
-1 & -2
\end{array}\right] , \left[\begin{array}{cc}
3 & 4 \\
-4 & -4
\end{array}\right] , \left[\begin{array}{cc}
-2 & -1 \\
4 & 4
\end{array}\right] , \left[\begin{array}{cc}
12 & 8 \\
-19 & -18
\end{array}\right] , \left[\begin{array}{cc}
4 & 4 \\
-3 & -2
\end{array}\right]\right\}. Be sure to explain why your result is a basis.
